              <p>A shorter version of the supplicative table prayer (also described in catalogues as prayer
                  over bread and wine of the Eucharist), <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5069Prayer"/>,
                                      cp. <bibl><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1935Formules"/>
